title: EP 144: Money, Power & Disrespect w/Doggie Diamonds

description:
We have the homie Doggie Diamonds sit in to talk about the recent rash of BS on the internet then we discuss why negativity is the new hustle.

For our fans in the UK, make sure you check James out on tour, and check out MC Eiht's new single ft KURUPT  "DOUBLE THAT"
